0.1.0.name: wordpress/browser-update-notify
0.1.0.description:
Inform your visitors unobtrusively to switch to a newer browser. Following browsers will be notified by default: IE:8&Older | Firefox:12&Older | Opera:11&Older |  Safari:5&Older | Chrome:auto | Source Code:Browser-Update.org. IE,FireFox,Safari notification levels can be modified.
This plugin is currently in beta
